&lt;p&gt;You likely started in consulting or another rigorous analytical environment, then moved into startups as a founder, early employee, or operator. You know how to build without a playbook, wear multiple hats, and ship quickly.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You’re hands-on, low ego, and highly resourceful. You use AI, automation, and modern tooling to create outsized leverage and move with speed. You can turn a blank page into a campaign, workflow, event, narrative, or system and iterate rapidly from there.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role works closely with the Head of Marketing and executive team as a force multiplier across the business. One week might include launching campaigns, testing growth experiments, building automations, supporting sales strategy, and executing executive events.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We move fast, priorities shift constantly, and adaptability is essential. You should thrive in high-intensity environments and be motivated by building something meaningful from the ground up.&lt;/p&gt;
